From 4ec98431edf7240b5682ebf4d9e9b1dbcb97f3cc Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Jay <studiosyakksol@gmail.com>
Date: Fri, 3 Apr 2026 12:49:05 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] fix: kill API 500s + Wren mission rewrite + icon update
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- price/route.ts: remove next:{revalidate} from fetch (root cause of 500s),
  add multi-endpoint DexScreener fallback (v1 + legacy), CORS headers,
  static fallback so UI never breaks
- stats/route.ts: same fix — remove next:{revalidate}, add in-memory 30s
  TTL cache, n8n → DexScreener v1 → legacy → fallback chain, CORS
- screener/route.ts: remove next:{revalidate} from fetch, graceful
  fallback instead of 502 when upstream fails
- Wren.tsx: full rewrite — reforestation/Wren.co removed, now UK
  grooming gang exposure + giving women a voice + funding investigations
- constants.ts: Wren icon 🌱 → 🛡️

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
---
